$DEC_ANEXOR

##---- Anexo R Q 04A - Informação económica
Local Char R04AR201(15)(1..1)
Local Char R04AR202(15)(1..1)
Local Char R04AR203(15)(1..1)
Local Char R04AR204(15)(1..1)
Local Char R04AR205(15)(1..1)
Local Char R04AR206(15)(1..1)
